<li class='cover' id='bookCover_18187013'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18187013-the-raven-king"><img alt="The Raven King (All for the Game, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1373489255l/18187013._SX98_.jpg" />
